# Admin Dashboard Navigation & Interconnection Plan

The objective is to establish logical, seamless navigation across all 10 workspace tabs within the single-page admin dashboard (`src/app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx`). Clicking on specific cards, status metrics, or table links will update state parameters (`setActiveTab`, `setSearch`, and `setFilter`) to route the admin to the relevant workflow screen.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> Since the admin panel is a single-page application tab system, all navigation is handled instantly client-side without full-page reloads. This keeps the experience extremely fast and responsive.

