## Verification Plan

### Automated Checks
- Run `npm run lint` or `npx eslint` to ensure no syntax errors.

### Manual Verification
- Verify cursor changes to `pointer` when hovering over connected cards.
- Click each connected card/link and check if it switches to the correct tab (and applies filters/searches where applicable).
